WEBVTT

00:00:28.036 --> 00:00:31.877
People love to invite me out all the time.

00:00:31.901 --> 00:00:33.307
Packed social life.

00:00:33.331 --> 00:00:36.395
Usually, when I talk
about this period of my life,

00:00:36.419 --> 00:00:39.633
the reaction I get is essentially:

00:00:39.657 --> 00:00:41.592
(Sighs)

00:00:41.616 --> 00:00:43.476
"I can't -- I can't imagine."

00:00:45.061 --> 00:00:46.595
But I do think you can.

00:00:47.696 --> 00:00:48.847
I think you can.

00:00:48.871 --> 00:00:50.238
And I think that you should

00:00:50.262 --> 00:00:52.879
because, someday,
it's going to happen to you.

00:00:52.903 --> 00:00:57.561
Maybe not these specific losses
in this specific order or at this speed,

00:00:57.585 --> 00:00:58.975
but like I said, I'm very fun

